{"title":"红军帽","authors":["林载华","江城"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林载华  剪纸  江城 配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年前暮春夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农红军渡金沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大军过后火种在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下军帽送彝家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红星闪闪照路程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似明灯心头挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此跟定共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出生入死打天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年前红军帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起大爹心头话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙后浪推前浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新苗出土又一茬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远记住红军帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘前辈洒血花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继承革命好传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗搞四化。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}